    "Allow ⌘ Esc to exit early": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "السماح بالخروج مبكرًا عبر ⌘ Esc"
          }
        },
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "⌘ Esc দিয়ে আগেই বের হওয়ার অনুমতি দিন"
          }
        },
        "tr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "⌘ Esc ile erken çıkışa izin ver"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "And establish prayer at the two ends of the day. Indeed, good deeds drive away evil deeds.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "وَأَقِمِ الصَّلَاةَ طَرَفَيِ النَّهَارِ، إِنَّ الْحَسَنَاتِ يُذْهِبْنَ السَّيِّئَاتِ."
          }
        },
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "দিনের দুই প্রান্তে নামাজ কায়েম করো; নিশ্চয়ই সৎকর্ম মন্দ কাজকে মুছে দেয়।"
          }
        },
        "tr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gündüzün iki ucunda namaz kıl; şüphesiz iyilikler kötülükleri giderir."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "And seek help through patience and prayer.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "وَاسْتَعِينُوا بِالصَّبْرِ وَالصَّلَاةِ."
          }
        },
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "আর ধৈর্য ও নামাজের মাধ্যমে সাহায্য প্রার্থনা করো।"
          }
        },
        "tr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sabır ve namazla yardım isteyin."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Angle-based": {
