    "Indeed, prayer has been decreed upon the believers a decree of specified times.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "إِنَّ الصَّلَاةَ كَانَتْ عَلَى الْمُؤْمِنِينَ كِتَابًا مَوْقُوتًا."
          }
        },
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "নিশ্চয়ই নামাজ মুমিনদের উপর নির্দিষ্ট সময়ে ফরজ করা হয়েছে।"
          }
        },
        "tr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Şüphesiz namaz, müminlere belirli vakitlerde farz kılınmıştır."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Indeed, prayer restrains from immorality and wrongdoing.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "إِنَّ الصَّلَاةَ تَنْهَىٰ عَنِ الْفَحْشَاءِ وَالْمُنْكَرِ."
          }
        },
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "নিশ্চয়ই নামাজ অশ্লীলতা ও মন্দ কাজ থেকে বিরত রাখে।"
          }
        },
        "tr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Şüphesiz namaz, hayâsızlıktan ve kötülükten alıkoyar."
          }
        }
      }
    },
