    "Takbir": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "تكبير"
          }
        },
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "তাকবির"
          }
        },
        "tr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tekbir"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The closest a servant is to his Lord is while prostrating.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "أَقْرَبُ مَا يَكُونُ الْعَبْدُ مِنْ رَبِّهِ وَهُوَ سَاجِدٌ."
          }
        },
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "বান্দা তার রবের সবচেয়ে নিকটবর্তী হয় সিজদারত অবস্থায়।"
          }
        },
        "tr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Kulun Rabbine en yakın olduğu an secde hâlidir."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The coolness of my eyes is in prayer.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "وَجُعِلَتْ قُرَّةُ عَيْنِي فِي الصَّلَاةِ."
          }
        },
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "আমার চোখের শীতলতা রাখা হয়েছে নামাজে।"
          }
        },
        "tr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gözümün nuru namazda kılındı."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The first deed for which a servant will be held accountable on the Day of Judgment is the prayer.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "أَوَّلُ مَا يُحَاسَبُ بِهِ الْعَبْدُ يَوْمَ الْقِيَامَةِ الصَّلَاةُ."
          }
        },
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "কিয়ামতের দিন বান্দার সর্বপ্রথম যে আমলের হিসাব নেওয়া হবে তা হলো নামাজ।"
          }
        },
        "tr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Kıyamet günü kulun hesaba çekileceği ilk amel namazdır."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Time left in current prayer": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "الوقت المتبقّي للصلاة الحالية"
          }
        },
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "বর্তমান নামাজের বাকি সময়"
          }
        },
        "tr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mevcut namazda kalan süre"
          }
        }
      }
    },
